room_title: Escape room "Alien Abduction" by Escape Room Virginia Peninsula in Newport News
room_address: 4410 East Claiborne Square, Suite 212 Hampton, VA 23666
room_description: You were abducted by a mysterious, flying ship and find yourself waking up in a cold laboratory with other humans. You’ve all been put in chains so that no one can escape. Surrounded by unusual tools and chemicals, it’s clear to see that the extraterrestrial creatures plan to experiment on you. The group must work together to free from the chains and escape before the experimentation begins!
